<plot>A timid man who has spent much of his life attempting without success to get out from under the domination of his mother, finds that marriage is no answer. His first wife is boring and traditional, and his second wife is trampish and crude. But what's worse than having to deal with each of them separately is when the three women join forces against him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?392622</url></doc>
